<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.7.11">
<l>āyarkulat tiṉilvantu tōṉṟiya vañcaṉa vaṇṇaṉṟaṉṉait</l>
<l>tāyarma kiḻavoṉ ṉārtaḷarat taḷarnaṭai naṭantataṉai</l>
<l>vēyarpu kaḻviṭṭu cittaṉcīrāl virittaṉa vuraikkavallār</l>
<l>māyaṉma ṇivaṇṇaṉ ṟāḷpaṇiyu makkaḷaip peṟuvarkaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master reciting [the verses] expounded with excellence</l>
<l>by the renowned Viṣṇu Cittaṉ of the Vēyars</l>
<l>about him with a black complexion</l>
<l>who was born in the clan of cowherds,</l>
<l>who came with a tottering walk so that</l>
<l>[his] mother rejoices [and his] enemies perish,</l>
<l>they will beget children who bow to the feet of the sapphire hued Māyaṉ.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
